cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM

The paper focuses on object detection using computer vision techniques, particularly for UAV applications. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also discusses the hardware and software architecture of the UAV platform, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics). The use of deep learning models and modified loss functions indicates that it could be relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the use of a dataset containing images and videos suggests that it could also be relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia).
